},{"pid":"6f79f3a903e8ca1c198de44e3fc1efb868021e48","tid":1692599,"uid":191049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:37:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"af392c7c74cf7d3c6e8eb82df8f9afa1d03db74a","tid":1692599,"uid":132283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:40:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"273f442655d70e881b4b34c3514b83b0f37b62ab","tid":1692599,"uid":151924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:41:40.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"c3b4dd301cd0896baf2122d9f2b5f262ae3a041d","tid":1692599,"uid":237581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:42:02.000Z","msg":"【二百萬三罷聯合陣線】<br />\n大家怨完呻完，想罷工，想了解點實行嘅，<br />\n可以入Channel參考吓。<br />\n成日話得我罷有咩用，咁俾多啲人都了解吓吖。<br />\n<br />\n⚠️常見問題⚠️<br />\n1. 幾時罷工呀？<br />\n其實罷工有好多前期準備工作，唔係定個日子就可以罷。一來要處理錢嘅問題，需要有罷工基金support，而罷工基金往往係由工會處理返自己個行業。二來要處理邊際成本嘅問題，例如成間公司得一個人罷，甚至有藍絲篤灰，老闆要炒話咁易，但如果成間公司有一半人罷工就好唔同。<br />\n<br />\n2. 咁點樣處理上述講嘅問題？<br />\n罷工好多時會有前期嘅行業行動，例如搵一日係網上call支持罷工嘅人集體dress code或者一齊戴朵花，又或者85三罷前嘅行業集會，咁你就可以由網絡延伸到real contact，知道實質你所處嘅職場有幾多係自己人，繼而組成組織，由自己working place去到隔離公司，甚至成個地區或行業。另一個方法就係工會，以成為會員嘅方式組成real contact，再用工會名義發起罷工。<br />\n<br />\n3. 我可以做啲咩？<br />\n幫手reach你自己行業嘅人，或者參與成立你所屬行業嘅工會。仲有share呢個群組出去，等呢度可以凝聚到更多有意有心罷工嘅人。<br />\n成立工會程序可參照&nbsp;<a href=\"https://t.me/hkonstrike/63\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkonstrike%2F63&d=yqGHcbR114BEm%2FDIyWJWfm%2FWCCUevL1oElw8znUqpaw%3D&h=4a2d2e28\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkonstrike/63</a><br />\n<br />\n4. 罷工基金點搞好？<br />\n目前主要有兩種聲音，一係眾籌，二係工會自己搞返自己行業嘅罷工基金。前者問題在於好難確認申請人係咪真係參與罷工定呃基金，而且如果個個行業人人都申請得，要處理極龐大嘅行政以及法律程序。相較之下，如果工會處理自身罷工基金可以免卻基金被濫用嘅問題，因為要會員先可以申請。當然，基金仍然需要好多討論。<br />\n<br />\n5. 呢個群組有咩用？<br />\n再次強調每個行業嘅組織、籌備工會或者工業行動要返返去自己個行業嗰度傾。但正因為行業太多，每個情況都唔同，所以呢個群組可以俾大家互通消息，最快知道各個行業嘅情況。同埋俾有心搞三罷嘅人可以係度集中討論。<br />\n<br />\n⚠️現設以下分台⚠️<br />\n三罷文宣小組&nbsp;<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/OUHilRRJw8V58N8AmwOrYw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FOUHilRRJw8V58N8AmwOrYw&d=yqGHcbR114BEm%2FDIyWJWfm%2FWCCUevL1oElw8znUqpaw%3D&h=53ccb8a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/OUHilRRJw8V58N8AmwOrYw</a><br />\n罷工基金討論台&nbsp;<a href=\"https://t.me/hkstrikefund\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkstrikefund&d=yqGHcbR114BEm%2FDIyWJWfm%2FWCCUevL1oElw8znUqpaw%3D&h=71f1c76a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkstrikefund</a><br />\n<br />\n🔴二百萬三罷聯合陣線🔴<br />\n抗爭 | 工會 | 罷工 | 行業行動<br />\n<br />\n頻道&nbsp;<a href=\"https://t.me/hkonstrike\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkonstrike&d=yqGHcbR114BEm%2FDIyWJWfm%2FWCCUevL1oElw8znUqpaw%3D&h=33acfd27\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkonstrike</a><br />\n公海&nbsp;<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/FhM2GRbY1ThsEzrnbEyduA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FFhM2GRbY1ThsEzrnbEyduA&d=yqGHcbR114BEm%2FDIyWJWfm%2FWCCUevL1oElw8znUqpaw%3D&h=65f400ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/FhM2GRbY1ThsEzrnbEyduA</a><br />\n(必讀)群組須知及group list&nbsp;<a href=\"https://t.me/hkonstrike/61\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkonstrike%2F61&d=yqGHcbR114BEm%2FDIyWJWfm%2FWCCUevL1oElw8znUqpaw%3D&h=8fec764f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkonstrike/61</a>"},{"pid":"8216933b17ce8357e9effdf48d26966cd5f2feab","tid":1692599,"uid":109780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:42:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88c32040e991103d2eba3e38efc7f68ba5a639e5","tid":1692599,"uid":259732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:42:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"